1
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:46,840
=Such A Good Love=

2
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:50,220
=Episode 20=

3
00:01:50,420 --> 00:01:52,700
(Summer 2012, Beijing)

4
00:01:52,710 --> 00:01:54,630
Hello, are you here to see Mr. Liao?

5
00:01:54,710 --> 00:01:55,070
Yes.

6
00:01:55,260 --> 00:01:55,740
This way.

7
00:01:57,430 --> 00:01:58,100
I'm sorry.

8
00:01:58,230 --> 00:01:59,950
Mr. Liao said
he's only meeting you alone.

9
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:02,660
No.

10
00:02:02,790 --> 00:02:03,430
It's fine.

11
00:02:03,660 --> 00:02:04,590
Wait for me outside.

12
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:07,020
Promise me

13
00:02:07,020 --> 00:02:09,820
you won't lay a hand on him,
no matter what he says.

14
00:02:09,820 --> 00:02:10,630
Don't worry.

15
00:02:11,030 --> 00:02:11,790
I know what to do.

16
00:02:12,580 --> 00:02:13,140
Wait for me.

17
00:02:13,860 --> 00:02:14,420
Okay.

18
00:02:21,380 --> 00:02:22,100
Please enter.

19
00:02:29,260 --> 00:02:30,580
I can't give you the 100,000 yuan

20
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:31,820
for car repairs right now.

21
00:02:33,100 --> 00:02:34,350
Give me a year.

22
00:02:34,980 --> 00:02:36,700
One year later,
I'll pay you with interest.

23
00:02:37,510 --> 00:02:39,960
Treat it as loaning me money
at a high interest rate for a year.

24
00:02:41,100 --> 00:02:43,750
I've fixed the car.
You don't have to bother anymore.

25
00:02:44,950 --> 00:02:45,700
What do you mean?

26
00:02:46,540 --> 00:02:47,140
Sit.

27
00:02:48,580 --> 00:02:50,030
I can afford this car.

28
00:02:50,420 --> 00:02:51,580
Can I not afford to fix it?

29
00:02:52,420 --> 00:02:54,080
Are you sure
I don't need to bother anymore?

30
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:55,750
It's over.

31
00:02:57,100 --> 00:02:57,910
Sit.

32
00:03:02,580 --> 00:03:03,700
Let's chat.

33
00:03:05,310 --> 00:03:06,310
Where are you from?

34
00:03:06,910 --> 00:03:08,420
A small place. Qinan.

35
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:09,910
Qinan old area?

36
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:13,630
That's one of the top ten
poorest counties in the country, right?

37
00:03:14,750 --> 00:03:15,380
Yes.

38
00:03:16,350 --> 00:03:18,950
My hometown
is also a small place and a poor county.

39
00:03:19,660 --> 00:03:21,860
Look.
Don't you think we're destined to meet?

40
00:03:23,350 --> 00:03:24,140
So to speak,

41
00:03:25,100 --> 00:03:26,910
you're the same as I was
when I was young.

42
00:03:27,350 --> 00:03:29,510
Your family is poor
and you can't stay there any longer.

43
00:03:29,510 --> 00:03:33,700
So you took a gamble and ran to Beijing.

44
00:03:34,070 --> 00:03:34,700
Right?

45
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:37,100
Who comes to Beijing
without wanting to make money?

46
00:03:37,260 --> 00:03:38,640
How much money do you want to make?

47
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:42,750
I have no idea.

48
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:45,140
Let me put it this way.

49
00:03:46,070 --> 00:03:47,700
You've been in Beijing for five years.

50
00:03:48,100 --> 00:03:52,030
How much money do you want to make
in the next five years?

51
00:03:54,310 --> 00:03:55,100
I have no idea.

52
00:03:55,700 --> 00:03:57,820
Think about it. Think about a number.

53
00:03:57,950 --> 00:03:58,860
Think big.

54
00:03:59,540 --> 00:04:00,380
I can't.

55
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:06,030
Let me help you.

56
00:04:07,820 --> 00:04:08,790
Here's 100,000 yuan.

57
00:04:09,100 --> 00:04:11,100
If you hit someone's Maybach,

58
00:04:11,580 --> 00:04:12,540
you'll get away with it.

59
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:15,510
Here's 200,000 yuan.

60
00:04:16,220 --> 00:04:18,380
It's enough to buy my watch.

61
00:04:18,380 --> 00:04:19,870
Don't underestimate this watch.

62
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:22,630
Wear it, and everyone will respect you.

63
00:04:25,820 --> 00:04:26,950
Here's 300,000 yuan.

64
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:29,580
It's enough
to buy you a nice little car.

65
00:04:29,950 --> 00:04:31,670
Don't ride
your crappy motorcycle anymore.

66
00:04:33,580 --> 00:04:34,780
Here's 400,000 yuan.

67
00:04:35,070 --> 00:04:36,340
If you go back to your hometown,

68
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:38,630
you can live a glorious life
for half your life.

69
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:40,630
Here's 500,000 yuan.

70
00:04:40,630 --> 00:04:44,070
It's enough
for you to open a gym in Yanjiao.

71
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:45,960
What's the meaning of this?

72
00:04:49,990 --> 00:04:51,380
Let's do business.

73
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:54,670
You can take

74
00:04:55,340 --> 00:04:56,510
this 500,000 yuan.

75
00:04:56,670 --> 00:04:57,950
Just tell Jingshu

76
00:04:58,260 --> 00:05:00,950
you want to break up
and ask her to be with me.

77
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:03,070
This statement

78
00:05:03,580 --> 00:05:04,870
will spare you

79
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,260
five years' effort.

80
00:05:08,840 --> 00:05:10,310
Are you bullying me because I'm poor?

81
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,360
Are you bullying me
for never seeing money?

82
00:05:13,430 --> 00:05:14,870
Let me tell you. I'm poor,

83
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:16,670
but I'm not desperate.

84
00:05:17,670 --> 00:05:19,580
Who cares about your filthy money?

85
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:23,950
Let me tell you.

86
00:05:24,220 --> 00:05:25,380
We're true love!

87
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,110
Do you understand true love?

88
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:29,340
I'll leave this money here.

89
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:32,510
If you think it through,
you can come back and get it anytime.

90
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:39,070
Who cares about your filthy money?

91
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:42,260
Let's go.

92
00:05:50,220 --> 00:05:51,950
Did you see his expression?

93
00:05:52,070 --> 00:05:52,950
Yes.

94
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:54,700
He looked stunned.

95
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:57,700
He thought he's all that for being rich.
How dare he tries to bribe me?

96
00:05:57,700 --> 00:05:58,460
Yeah!

97
00:05:58,750 --> 00:05:59,630
Get lost!

98
00:06:00,110 --> 00:06:00,870
Watch out!

99
00:06:09,950 --> 00:06:10,750
Jingshu.

100
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:13,460
I love you.

101
00:06:14,990 --> 00:06:15,950
I love you too.

102
00:06:17,820 --> 00:06:20,310
500,000 yuan.

103
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:21,460
You trampled it underfoot.

104
00:06:22,220 --> 00:06:23,380
You resisted temptation

105
00:06:23,990 --> 00:06:25,310
and withstood the test.

106
00:06:25,870 --> 00:06:27,220
Why didn't you praise Jingshu?

107
00:06:27,260 --> 00:06:29,020
Jingshu withstood the test.

108
00:06:29,460 --> 00:06:31,430
That rich guy
has pursued her for a long time.

109
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:33,750
She didn't waver.

110
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,900
Here, a toast to you two.

111
00:06:34,900 --> 00:06:35,800
A toast to you two.

112
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:37,380
- A toast to love.
- A toast to love.

113
00:06:37,550 --> 00:06:38,220
Here.

114
00:06:38,340 --> 00:06:39,630
If I wrote your story

115
00:06:39,950 --> 00:06:41,460
into a movie script,

116
00:06:41,460 --> 00:06:42,870
many people would want to watch it.

117
00:06:43,110 --> 00:06:44,780
Two youths with nothing.

118
00:06:45,220 --> 00:06:47,020
500,000 yuan, Dumbbell.

119
00:06:47,020 --> 00:06:48,750
- 500,000 yuan.
- 500,000 yuan.

120
00:06:48,990 --> 00:06:50,020
You trampled it underfoot.

121
00:06:50,380 --> 00:06:51,900
You treat money like dirt.

122
00:06:52,380 --> 00:06:53,460
What a great story.

123
00:06:53,460 --> 00:06:54,340
The story is great,

124
00:06:54,340 --> 00:06:55,870
but you can't curse them.

125
00:06:55,950 --> 00:06:57,700
What do you mean they have nothing?

126
00:06:57,780 --> 00:06:59,340
- Right?
- Zhou Shui is right.

127
00:06:59,340 --> 00:07:00,460
We have nothing.

128
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:01,630
We have no money.

129
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:02,990
If I had money,

130
00:07:02,990 --> 00:07:04,020
this won't happen.

131
00:07:04,020 --> 00:07:05,580
Who says we have nothing?

132
00:07:05,580 --> 00:07:06,870
I have you, and you have me.

133
00:07:06,870 --> 00:07:08,340
And those things are over.

134
00:07:08,340 --> 00:07:09,000
Here we go again.

135
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:09,820
We should look ahead.

136
00:07:09,820 --> 00:07:11,600
- We want to be together forever.
- How boring.

137
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:11,840
Right?

138
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:12,340
Yes.

139
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:15,950
I envy them so much.

140
00:07:16,020 --> 00:07:17,140
What do you mean?

141
00:07:17,670 --> 00:07:19,550
I envy her boyfriend.

142
00:07:19,550 --> 00:07:21,430
Look how reliable her boyfriend is.

143
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:22,510
I'm unreliable?

144
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:23,480
You're not very reliable.

145
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,040
If it were you,
you'll give a 50% discount

146
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,190
and sell me for 200,000 yuan.

147
00:07:26,820 --> 00:07:27,870
You think so little of me.

148
00:07:27,870 --> 00:07:28,760
How much will you sell?

149
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:31,960
Do you think I'm the type
to get taken advantage of?

150
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:34,560
- Really? What type are you then?
- How much will you sell her for?

151
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:34,820
30.

152
00:07:35,220 --> 00:07:36,340
Do you have any self-respect?

153
00:07:36,630 --> 00:07:37,780
Do you have any self-respect?

154
00:07:37,950 --> 00:07:39,630
You're really...
I'll drag you to the market

155
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:41,320
and sell you
for four yuan per kilo.

156
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:43,720
Let me calculate. I weigh 70 kilograms.
280 yuan is alright.

157
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,600
You have to be deboned.

158
00:07:45,310 --> 00:07:47,310
Here, let's toast to our worth.

159
00:07:47,310 --> 00:07:49,110
- A toast to our worth.
- A toast to our worth.

160
00:08:05,110 --> 00:08:07,160
(Swimming Training)
My resume and coaching certificate.

161
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,140
Can you give me a chance?

162
00:08:10,340 --> 00:08:12,870
You worked at Tera Wellness before.

163
00:08:14,070 --> 00:08:15,990
How many members
have you accumulated there?

164
00:08:15,990 --> 00:08:17,140
How many can you bring over?

165
00:08:18,460 --> 00:08:20,780
I worked there for only a few months.

166
00:08:21,340 --> 00:08:22,750
Why?

167
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:24,820
Something happened at home,
so I had no choice.

168
00:08:25,580 --> 00:08:27,430
If something happens at home again,

169
00:08:27,430 --> 00:08:28,700
will you leave again?

170
00:08:28,700 --> 00:08:29,510
No.

171
00:08:29,510 --> 00:08:30,750
Nothing will happen again.

172
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:34,100
You have no education and no resources.

173
00:08:34,100 --> 00:08:35,430
You can't even stick to a job.

174
00:08:35,620 --> 00:08:37,390
Sorry, we can't hire you.

175
00:08:43,501 --> 00:08:45,580
(Commercial Proposal)

176
00:08:59,270 --> 00:09:01,390
Mr. Li, we'll pay attention

177
00:09:01,390 --> 00:09:02,670
to your company's commercial.

178
00:09:02,950 --> 00:09:05,340
Its priority is absolutely top one.

179
00:09:05,340 --> 00:09:06,670
(General Manager's Office)

180
00:09:06,670 --> 00:09:07,670
This project

181
00:09:07,700 --> 00:09:10,310
is also our company's key project, okay?

182
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:11,270
Don't worry.

183
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:12,980
We won't let you down.

184
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:15,340
Come in.

185
00:09:18,220 --> 00:09:18,980
Zhaoyang.

186
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:20,460
Hello, Mr. Li.

187
00:09:20,620 --> 00:09:21,950
I'm Director Zhou Shui.

188
00:09:21,950 --> 00:09:23,560
- Hello.
- Zhaoyang said you were coming.

189
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:24,860
I made a commercial proposal.

190
00:09:24,860 --> 00:09:25,620
Take a look.

191
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:28,240
If you have any questions, let me know.
I can amend it at any time.

192
00:09:31,100 --> 00:09:32,100
Not bad.

193
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:36,220
The proposal is pretty good.

194
00:09:37,220 --> 00:09:38,790
You value me very much, Mr. Zhaoyang.

195
00:09:39,100 --> 00:09:40,790
How sincere. Look.

196
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:42,980
We have to show some sincerity, right?

197
00:09:42,980 --> 00:09:43,700
Mr. Li.

198
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:47,100
I would like to take this opportunity
to introduce you

199
00:09:47,150 --> 00:09:50,340
to our talented Director Zhou Shui.

200
00:09:51,220 --> 00:09:53,270
He's capable and tasteful.

201
00:09:53,310 --> 00:09:55,860
You'll have nothing to worry
if you hand this commercial to him.

202
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:58,030
Okay, you're young and promising.

203
00:09:58,030 --> 00:09:59,430
Thank you. I will try my best.

204
00:09:59,430 --> 00:09:59,860
Okay?

205
00:10:00,340 --> 00:10:00,920
Don't worry.

206
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:03,320
I will complete this commercial
with high quality and on time.

207
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:05,100
I'll make sure you're satisfied.
Rest assured.

208
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:07,820
I'm very satisfied with this proposal.

209
00:10:07,820 --> 00:10:10,500
Not bad, Zhou Shui.
You leveraged your strengths this time.

210
00:10:10,950 --> 00:10:12,100
You have to trust Mr. Li.

211
00:10:12,100 --> 00:10:12,910
I think everyone

212
00:10:12,910 --> 00:10:14,550
- can't be wrong about your taste.
- Here.

213
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:14,820
Okay.

214
00:10:14,820 --> 00:10:15,840
I'm counting on you.

215
00:10:15,880 --> 00:10:16,550
- Okay.
- Goodbye.

216
00:10:16,550 --> 00:10:17,550
Right here. Goodbye.

217
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:17,860
Okay.

218
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:18,270
Bye.

219
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:18,910
Okay.

220
00:10:19,700 --> 00:10:20,500
Not bad.

221
00:10:39,910 --> 00:10:40,670
Zhaoyang.

222
00:10:41,390 --> 00:10:44,640
My poor work attitude before
caused you trouble.

223
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:46,950
I also have to reflect on myself.

224
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:50,100
I admit that I've been careless
in handling some matters recently.

225
00:10:50,820 --> 00:10:51,950
I hope you don't mind.

226
00:10:53,390 --> 00:10:54,190
Anyway,

227
00:10:54,340 --> 00:10:56,220
I'll rely on you to support me.

228
00:10:56,740 --> 00:10:59,120
You respect me.
How could I let you suffer?

229
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,910
The budget for this commercial
is 100,000 yuan.

230
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,740
Make good use of it.

231
00:11:02,070 --> 00:11:04,120
You can have what's left of the budget
as your bonus.

232
00:11:05,580 --> 00:11:06,620
Don't tell anyone else.

233
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:12,150
Time to get off work!

234
00:11:15,620 --> 00:11:16,950
The sun is great today.

235
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:18,860
You're acting weird.

236
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,520
- What's the matter?
- Why are you

237
00:11:22,460 --> 00:11:24,700
so positive and motivated today?

238
00:11:25,190 --> 00:11:26,910
You're so shameless.

239
00:11:27,910 --> 00:11:28,500
Shameless?

240
00:11:29,150 --> 00:11:29,980
How shameless.

241
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,120
How can we make money
without being shameless?

242
00:11:33,950 --> 00:11:34,980
Zhaoyang said

243
00:11:34,980 --> 00:11:36,680
the budget for this project
is 100,000 yuan.

244
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:38,910
Excluding all costs,
there are 8,000 or 9,000 yuan left.

245
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:40,430
It's all ours.

246
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:41,500
8,000 or 9,000 yuan?

247
00:11:42,030 --> 00:11:42,860
That's a lot.

248
00:11:44,670 --> 00:11:47,100
But when have you ever calculated money?

249
00:11:47,550 --> 00:11:48,620
Did something trigger you?

250
00:11:49,620 --> 00:11:50,620
No.

251
00:11:50,620 --> 00:11:51,980
I think I figured it out.

252
00:11:53,030 --> 00:11:54,220
I promised your mom

253
00:11:54,950 --> 00:11:57,670
to make money, move to Beijing,

254
00:11:57,700 --> 00:11:59,550
live in a better house,
drive a better car,

255
00:11:59,550 --> 00:12:00,910
and give you a better life.

256
00:12:01,910 --> 00:12:02,670
So I can't be

257
00:12:02,670 --> 00:12:04,150
so willful anymore.

258
00:12:06,700 --> 00:12:07,820
But I still think

259
00:12:07,820 --> 00:12:09,460
you're cuter when you're willful.

260
00:12:11,910 --> 00:12:13,030
Am I not cute now?

261
00:12:13,190 --> 00:12:14,910
You're cute. Very cute.

262
00:12:15,150 --> 00:12:18,340
But it's a puppy-like cuteness.

263
00:12:19,100 --> 00:12:20,220
It doesn't sound good.

264
00:12:20,390 --> 00:12:21,550
It's not.

265
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:25,310
Why is the sun so good today?

266
00:12:25,310 --> 00:12:27,950
Why do I feel so relaxed?

267
00:12:29,460 --> 00:12:31,460
I guess it's because I've grown up.

268
00:12:32,740 --> 00:12:33,820
Where's my computer?

269
00:12:35,760 --> 00:12:36,860
I didn't take the computer.

270
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:39,980
Your previous budget of 300,000 yuan

271
00:12:39,980 --> 00:12:41,150
isn't feasible.

272
00:12:41,580 --> 00:12:42,550
300,000 yuan?

273
00:12:43,270 --> 00:12:45,950
When have I, Lai Zhaoyang,
shoot a small project worth 300,000 yuan?

274
00:12:45,950 --> 00:12:48,150
Look, the script
was written by our creative director,

275
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:49,500
Director Zhou Shui.

276
00:12:49,500 --> 00:12:51,070
