00:27:19,600 --> 00:27:20,500
Open a clothing store?

552
00:27:21,320 --> 00:27:22,760
Do you want to open a clothing store?

553
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:25,700
Let's open a huge clothing store.

554
00:27:26,110 --> 00:27:27,300
Let's disappear.

555
00:27:28,020 --> 00:27:29,220
We can even change our name

556
00:27:29,220 --> 00:27:30,830
and never come to Beijing again.

557
00:27:46,830 --> 00:27:48,300
Are you moved by what I said?

558
00:27:51,220 --> 00:27:53,150
If you really
want that one million yuan,

559
00:27:55,430 --> 00:27:56,430
just take it.

560
00:27:57,740 --> 00:27:58,540
Okay.

561
00:28:00,390 --> 00:28:01,190
Okay.

562
00:28:02,390 --> 00:28:04,190
I want the one million yuan.

563
00:28:06,980 --> 00:28:08,060
That's your money.

564
00:28:10,460 --> 00:28:11,630
It has nothing to do with me.

565
00:28:15,950 --> 00:28:17,190
I won't go with you.

566
00:28:18,260 --> 00:28:19,190
What do you mean?

567
00:28:20,430 --> 00:28:22,740
Where else can you go
if you don't go with me?

568
00:28:25,110 --> 00:28:26,190
I'm not going anywhere.

569
00:28:30,020 --> 00:28:32,500
I never thought about leaving here.

570
00:29:01,390 --> 00:29:02,980
The sunset is so beautiful today.

571
00:29:59,670 --> 00:30:00,390
Here, Daji.

572
00:30:01,460 --> 00:30:02,260
Zhaoyang.

573
00:30:02,300 --> 00:30:03,150
You worked hard.

574
00:30:03,220 --> 00:30:04,460
You worked hard.

575
00:30:07,720 --> 00:30:09,060
I have something good to show you.

576
00:30:10,020 --> 00:30:11,700
I just confirmed

577
00:30:12,060 --> 00:30:13,740
the new office for our company.

578
00:30:14,060 --> 00:30:14,670
Take a look.

579
00:30:17,430 --> 00:30:19,460
Look. It's the building next door.

580
00:30:20,390 --> 00:30:22,950
Thirty-third floor.
Look at the natural lighting.

581
00:30:23,150 --> 00:30:24,980
We've got half the floor
all to ourselves.

582
00:30:25,440 --> 00:30:27,670
Look out, and China World Trade Center
is right across us.

583
00:30:27,670 --> 00:30:29,630
I've reserved a room for you.

584
00:30:29,780 --> 00:30:30,590
When the time comes,

585
00:30:31,260 --> 00:30:33,110
we'll put a nameplate on the door.

586
00:30:33,430 --> 00:30:34,700
Planning Director.

587
00:30:35,540 --> 00:30:36,350
What do you think?

588
00:30:37,870 --> 00:30:38,460
Here.

589
00:30:40,430 --> 00:30:41,300
Thank you, Zhaoyang.

590
00:30:49,300 --> 00:30:50,700
Don't you have something to tell me?

591
00:30:51,020 --> 00:30:51,670
Yes.

592
00:30:52,020 --> 00:30:53,430
Go ahead. What is it?

593
00:30:57,430 --> 00:30:59,870
Zhou Shui and I both know

594
00:30:59,870 --> 00:31:02,260
you were the one
who brought us out of Shendu

595
00:31:02,260 --> 00:31:03,460
and started a business with us.

596
00:31:03,460 --> 00:31:04,910
You gave us so many opportunities.

597
00:31:05,110 --> 00:31:06,870
You've been very kind to us.

598
00:31:07,830 --> 00:31:09,350
We're really grateful.

599
00:31:10,460 --> 00:31:12,950
But after careful consideration,

600
00:31:13,780 --> 00:31:14,700
we decided...

601
00:31:14,720 --> 00:31:16,880
What's the matter?
You don't want to work for me anymore?

602
00:31:17,150 --> 00:31:18,220
You want to quit, right?

603
00:31:19,670 --> 00:31:20,870
I'm sorry, Zhaoyang.

604
00:31:23,500 --> 00:31:24,700
It's Zhou Shui's idea, right?

605
00:31:25,780 --> 00:31:26,460
No.

606
00:31:27,350 --> 00:31:29,870
We discussed it
and made the decision together.

607
00:31:31,430 --> 00:31:33,430
Did you and Zhou Shui
get together in college?

608
00:31:34,350 --> 00:31:34,910
Yes.

609
00:31:36,540 --> 00:31:37,460
I can imagine it.

610
00:31:38,350 --> 00:31:39,430
When you were in college,

611
00:31:39,500 --> 00:31:40,590
people like Zhou Shui

612
00:31:41,630 --> 00:31:43,950
have talent, good personality

613
00:31:43,950 --> 00:31:45,830
and free-spirited.

614
00:31:45,830 --> 00:31:46,190
Yes.

615
00:31:46,190 --> 00:31:48,190
He's also a perfectionist.

616
00:31:48,260 --> 00:31:50,670
If he's a little romantic,
many girls will fall for him.

617
00:31:50,910 --> 00:31:51,300
Yes.

618
00:31:51,300 --> 00:31:52,980
Especially to little girls.

619
00:31:53,220 --> 00:31:54,590
He's still quite charming.

620
00:31:54,700 --> 00:31:55,500
But

621
00:31:56,780 --> 00:31:59,300
you're no longer a little girl.

622
00:32:03,220 --> 00:32:05,110
Yes, I'm almost 30.

623
00:32:06,950 --> 00:32:07,740
That's why

624
00:32:08,190 --> 00:32:10,910
you should think more about
yourself when you're young.

625
00:32:11,740 --> 00:32:12,780
Follow the right person,

626
00:32:13,300 --> 00:32:14,870
and you're halfway to success.

627
00:32:15,360 --> 00:32:16,350
Follow the wrong person,

628
00:32:17,060 --> 00:32:18,020
you'll harm yourself.

629
00:32:19,780 --> 00:32:20,590
Daji.

630
00:32:21,670 --> 00:32:22,830
I noticed a long time ago.

631
00:32:23,300 --> 00:32:24,220
You're capable

632
00:32:24,910 --> 00:32:26,220
but more ambitious.

633
00:32:27,220 --> 00:32:29,300
Follow me, I won't mistreat you.

634
00:32:33,260 --> 00:32:34,060
I know.

635
00:32:34,670 --> 00:32:36,460
You're only Planning Director for now.

636
00:32:37,460 --> 00:32:39,670
Maybe the company
will be yours in the future.

637
00:32:41,390 --> 00:32:42,190
Don't quit.

638
00:32:42,670 --> 00:32:43,460
Stay.

639
00:32:46,260 --> 00:32:48,700
If I stay, what about Zhou Shui?

640
00:32:55,110 --> 00:32:57,350
I think you don't
fully understand what I said.

641
00:33:01,020 --> 00:33:01,670
Daji.

642
00:33:02,910 --> 00:33:03,980
What I just said

643
00:33:04,540 --> 00:33:06,350
was only meant for you.

644
00:33:07,460 --> 00:33:08,630
I don't know why either.

645
00:33:10,190 --> 00:33:11,220
Whenever I see you,

646
00:33:12,200 --> 00:33:14,430
I keep thinking of the girl
who strived with me in Beijing

647
00:33:14,430 --> 00:33:16,150
but eventually separated.

648
00:33:17,950 --> 00:33:19,670
I don't want to regret it again.

649
00:33:20,390 --> 00:33:22,390
Can you help me make up
for my past regrets

650
00:33:22,910 --> 00:33:24,260
and create

651
00:33:25,110 --> 00:33:26,150
a different future with me?

652
00:33:34,540 --> 00:33:35,350
What do you think?

653
00:33:52,350 --> 00:33:53,220
You know what?

654
00:33:53,910 --> 00:33:55,260
You mentioned Zhou Shui

655
00:33:55,260 --> 00:33:56,700
and said so much.

656
00:33:57,910 --> 00:33:59,540
But when Zhou Shui described you,

657
00:34:00,540 --> 00:34:02,500
he hit the nail on the head
in just one sentence.

658
00:34:02,630 --> 00:34:03,460
What did he say?

659
00:34:04,110 --> 00:34:05,060
He said,

660
00:34:05,500 --> 00:34:07,540
"Don't think he's a good person."

661
00:34:14,710 --> 00:34:16,460
I'm officially informing you

662
00:34:16,620 --> 00:34:20,100
that Zhou Shui and I are resigning.
We quit.

663
00:34:21,390 --> 00:34:23,580
Do you really like him that much?

664
00:34:28,310 --> 00:34:29,500
I don't just like him.

665
00:34:30,960 --> 00:34:32,230
Because the most important thing

666
00:34:32,230 --> 00:34:34,180
about being a girlfriend is loyalty.

667
00:34:34,660 --> 00:34:36,390
Don't you always mention

668
00:34:36,830 --> 00:34:38,180
the girl you lost?

669
00:34:40,310 --> 00:34:41,750
I believe that girl

670
00:34:42,160 --> 00:34:44,310
definitely didn't treat you like this
at the beginning.

671
00:34:47,390 --> 00:34:48,500
Goodbye, Zhaoyang.

672
00:35:01,390 --> 00:35:03,750
Eggs, spinach,

673
00:35:03,750 --> 00:35:06,620
beef, chili, tomato.

674
00:35:06,830 --> 00:35:07,620
Ambush!

675
00:35:08,600 --> 00:35:09,360
What are you doing?

676
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:11,000
You scared me. Daji, what are you doing?

677
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:12,160
What did I do? I ambushed you.

678
00:35:12,180 --> 00:35:13,660
I thought I was being robbed.

679
00:35:13,660 --> 00:35:14,870
What can I rob from you?

680
00:35:15,580 --> 00:35:16,350
My eggs.

681
00:35:16,350 --> 00:35:17,870
What's so good about your eggs?

682
00:35:17,870 --> 00:35:18,950
I bought five eggs

683
00:35:18,950 --> 00:35:19,660
and beef.

684
00:35:19,660 --> 00:35:21,540
I'm going to make beef fried eggs today.

685
00:35:21,540 --> 00:35:23,140
Is this a good combination?

686
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:24,500
Is it not possible?

687
00:35:24,500 --> 00:35:25,180
I don't think so.

688
00:35:25,180 --> 00:35:25,910
Fine.

689
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:27,910
Stir-fry them together.

690
00:35:27,910 --> 00:35:28,870
I'm just kidding.

691
00:35:30,710 --> 00:35:31,980
How did it go? Are you done?

692
00:35:33,200 --> 00:35:34,680
You're really good at judging people.

693
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:37,880
I should have listened to you
from the beginning.

694
00:35:39,310 --> 00:35:40,100
What do you mean?

695
00:35:40,870 --> 00:35:41,660
Nothing.

696
00:35:42,620 --> 00:35:43,460
I love you.

697
00:35:44,910 --> 00:35:46,060
You're very strange today.

698
00:35:48,270 --> 00:35:49,060
I love you too.

699
00:35:51,180 --> 00:35:51,800
Is lettuce okay?

700
00:35:51,800 --> 00:35:53,240
- Sure.
- Stir-fry lettuce with garlic.

701
00:35:53,240 --> 00:35:54,200
Stir-fry some vegetables.

702
00:35:54,200 --> 00:35:55,240
Why are the lights not on?

703
00:35:56,750 --> 00:35:57,540
Gosh.

704
00:35:58,020 --> 00:35:58,750
Dumbbell.

705
00:35:58,750 --> 00:36:00,270
What happened? Are you drunk?

706
00:36:03,350 --> 00:36:05,460
I bought the quilt and pillow
when I moved in.

707
00:36:05,800 --> 00:36:07,640
I don't need it anymore.
I'll leave them to you.

708
00:36:07,640 --> 00:36:08,060
Jingshu.

709
00:36:08,060 --> 00:36:09,950
Jingshu, what happened to you guys?

710
00:36:10,580 --> 00:36:12,140
This bottle of bath gel is new.

711
00:36:12,600 --> 00:36:14,500
The replacement
is in the cabinet under the sink.

712
00:36:14,500 --> 00:36:16,080
Remember to replace it
once you finish it.

713
00:36:16,080 --> 00:36:16,750
What's going on?

714
00:36:16,750 --> 00:36:18,320
What's going on? Jingshu, what happened?

715
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:20,840
Electricity and internet fees
are due on the 10th of every month.

716
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:21,680
I've paid this month.

717
00:36:23,120 --> 00:36:24,760
There are some winter clothes
in the closet.

718
00:36:24,760 --> 00:36:25,800
I don't want them anymore.

719
00:36:25,910 --> 00:36:26,390
No. Jingshu.

720
00:36:26,390 --> 00:36:28,000
It's up to you
to sell or throw them away.

721
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:29,560
No, what are you doing? Are you leaving?

722
00:36:30,440 --> 00:36:31,240
I'm leaving.

723
00:36:31,240 --> 00:36:33,120
- Are you going back to your hometown?
- Jingshu.

724
00:36:33,910 --> 00:36:35,710
Do you think I'm that useless?

725
00:36:36,180 --> 00:36:37,390
No, you... No.

726
00:36:37,390 --> 00:36:38,430
Did you two argue?

727
00:36:38,830 --> 00:36:39,580
What's going on?

728
00:36:41,180 --> 00:36:42,350
Dumbbell, Jingshu is leaving.

729
00:36:42,350 --> 00:36:42,790
Hurry up.

730
00:36:42,790 --> 00:36:44,350
Get up.

731
00:36:44,350 --> 00:36:45,230
Go after her!

732
00:36:45,460 --> 00:36:46,620
Are you a man?

733
00:36:46,950 --> 00:36:48,870
Dumbbell, get up. Hurry.

734
00:36:50,100 --> 00:36:50,750
Get up!

735
00:36:50,750 --> 00:36:51,620
Jingshu, you...

736
00:36:52,310 --> 00:36:52,870
Jingshu!

737
00:36:53,240 --> 00:36:53,870
What's going on?

738
00:36:53,870 --> 00:36:54,720
Get up. Are you a man?

739
00:36:54,720 --> 00:36:55,240
No, Dumbbell.

740
00:36:55,240 --> 00:36:56,520
- Go after her!
- What's going on?

741
00:36:56,520 --> 00:36:57,040
Are you a man?

742
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:58,060
Don't touch me!

743
00:37:00,180 --> 00:37:01,710
I'm not a man anymore!

744
00:37:03,060 --> 00:37:04,500
I sold her for one million yuan.

745
00:37:04,500 --> 00:37:05,540
Are you satisfied now?

746
00:37:10,710 --> 00:37:11,500
Jingshu.

747
00:37:12,020 --> 00:37:13,180
You lost your mind!

748
00:37:15,500 --> 00:37:16,180
Jingshu!

749
00:37:50,660 --> 00:37:51,830
- Shen Jingshu!
- Jingshu!

750
00:37:53,140 --> 00:37:55,960
Are you really leaving with that person?
Can you have some self-respect?

751
00:37:57,310 --> 00:37:58,100
Shen Jingshu.

752
00:37:58,400 --> 00:38:00,430
You let a fitness coach
sold you for a million yuan.

753
00:38:00,430 --> 00:38:01,390
You're incapable.

754
00:38:01,950 --> 00:38:03,430
Sell him if you're capable.

755
00:38:03,430 --> 00:38:04,390
Why are you leaving?

756
00:38:05,270 --> 00:38:06,710
- Shen Jingshu!
- Shen Jingshu!

757
00:38:06,870 --> 00:38:08,270
I dare you to take another step.

758
00:38:08,830 --> 00:38:10,390
If you dare to get into the car, try it.

759
00:38:11,710 --> 00:38:14,830
If you dare to get into the car,
we're no longer friends!

760
00:38:15,540 --> 00:38:17,020
Don't contact me anymore!

761
00:38:23,790 --> 00:38:24,660
Shen Jingshu!

762
00:38:34,270 --> 00:38:35,060
Daji.

763
00:38:36,180 --> 00:38:37,500
Let me tell you a secret.

764
00:38:39,950 --> 00:38:41,830
My name isn't Shen Jingshu.

765
00:38:43,660 --> 00:38:44,870
My name is Luo Guixi.

766
00:38:46,950 --> 00:38:48,910
Shen Jingshu is someone else.

767
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:52,840
