Hello everyone, my name is Shen Jingshu.

768
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:54,820
My name is taken from Classic of Poetry.

769
00:38:54,830 --> 00:38:57,500
"I waited for a girl at the city corner.

770
00:38:57,500 --> 00:38:59,910
Loving her but not seeing her.
I scratch my head and hesitate."

771
00:39:01,020 --> 00:39:02,540
Shen Jingshu spoke very well.

772
00:39:02,540 --> 00:39:04,020
Come on, next student.

773
00:39:07,460 --> 00:39:10,060
Hello, everyone. My name is Luo Guixi.

774
00:39:10,500 --> 00:39:12,580
My name was given by a fortune teller.

775
00:39:12,660 --> 00:39:14,980
The fortune teller
said I would be rich...

776
00:39:14,980 --> 00:39:17,620
Luo Guixi? How are you rich?

777
00:39:17,620 --> 00:39:19,750
You should be called Luo Qiongxi.

778
00:39:21,660 --> 00:39:22,960
