779
00:39:22,960 --> 00:39:23,430
Silence.

780
00:39:24,980 --> 00:39:25,790
Silence!

781
00:39:28,270 --> 00:39:29,060
Silence.

782
00:39:30,140 --> 00:39:30,950
Silence!

783
00:39:38,500 --> 00:39:39,580
(Exercise Book, Luo Guixi)

784
00:39:39,580 --> 00:39:48,620
(Shen Jingshu)

785
00:40:04,830 --> 00:40:05,620
No.

786
00:40:07,270 --> 00:40:08,060
Jingshu.

787
00:40:13,020 --> 00:40:15,660
I don't care if your name
is Luo Guixi or Shen Jingshu.

788
00:40:16,100 --> 00:40:17,830
You should be true to yourself.

789
00:40:19,390 --> 00:40:21,140
You will definitely
have a better choice.

790
00:40:21,140 --> 00:40:22,500
A better choice?

791
00:40:25,790 --> 00:40:26,580
Daji.

792
00:40:28,390 --> 00:40:29,950
I never had a choice.

793
00:40:32,100 --> 00:40:33,710
I just want to stay in Beijing.

794
00:40:34,430 --> 00:40:36,230
But you're going to sell yourself now.

795
00:40:37,270 --> 00:40:39,020
What's the point
of you staying in Beijing?

796
00:40:42,620 --> 00:40:44,230
I know you want to stay in Beijing,

797
00:40:44,870 --> 00:40:46,310
but there are many ways

798
00:40:46,310 --> 00:40:47,580
to stay in Beijing, right?

799
00:40:48,310 --> 00:40:50,390
Maybe we haven't worked hard enough.

800
00:40:50,620 --> 00:40:51,830
Let's work harder.

801
00:40:52,460 --> 00:40:54,270
Even if we push just a little harder,

802
00:40:54,270 --> 00:40:54,790
maybe we...

803
00:40:54,790 --> 00:40:55,270
Jingshu.

804
00:40:55,270 --> 00:40:57,270
We can stay here by our own means,
right?

805
00:40:57,270 --> 00:40:58,350
Let's work together.

806
00:40:58,460 --> 00:40:59,980
We can make it in Beijing.

807
00:40:59,980 --> 00:41:00,870
Do you believe that?

808
00:41:07,460 --> 00:41:08,270
Jingshu.

809
00:41:12,270 --> 00:41:13,060
Jingshu.

810
00:41:14,950 --> 00:41:15,750
Jingshu.

811
00:42:38,750 --> 00:42:40,180
(Dumbbell said before he left)

812
00:42:41,060 --> 00:42:42,390
(that he loves Jingshu very much.)

813
00:42:44,060 --> 00:42:45,100
(But many times)

814
00:42:46,100 --> 00:42:47,390
(he couldn't figure her out,)

815
00:42:48,660 --> 00:42:50,580
(just like how he
couldn't understand Beijing.)

816
00:42:52,500 --> 00:42:55,540
(Until this one million yuan
ruined their love,)

817
00:42:57,140 --> 00:42:58,910
(he still couldn't figure out Jingshu.)

818
00:43:00,870 --> 00:43:01,910
(But this time)

819
00:43:03,270 --> 00:43:05,020
(he saw himself for who he really is.)

820
00:43:33,480 --> 00:43:36,640
Please, put away your compromises

821
00:43:37,360 --> 00:43:41,340
Get closer to the ideal world

822
00:43:41,340 --> 00:43:46,590
Even if that day
comes a little slower and lonelier

823
00:43:48,400 --> 00:43:51,710
A person's broken copper and iron

824
00:43:52,200 --> 00:43:55,670
Still has to be forged
into their own sword

825
00:43:56,090 --> 00:44:00,320
Dare to scorn, dare to be passionate,
dare to write

