00:44:05,520 --> 00:44:09,650
The brave person says goodbye first

828
00:44:09,820 --> 00:44:13,450
The love that's worth it
is always sorry

829
00:44:13,550 --> 00:44:17,230
Once we were bold and fearless,
fighting against the world

830
00:44:17,480 --> 00:44:20,860
Only later realizing
how small and pitiful we were

831
00:44:20,860 --> 00:44:24,870
The brave person says goodbye

832
00:44:25,040 --> 00:44:28,720
The love that's worth it
still leaves us in debt

833
00:44:28,950 --> 00:44:32,280
If we were more cautious
and didn't take risks back then

834
00:44:32,280 --> 00:44:35,680
We might have our own fatigue

835
00:44:35,900 --> 00:44:38,110
Don't long for it

836
00:44:39,990 --> 00:44:43,220
Please answer me, I want to understand

837
00:44:44,160 --> 00:44:47,980
Love is worth the passion,
worth the dark night

838
00:44:47,980 --> 00:44:54,180
Worth the stubbornness
to light up moments of flickering light

839
00:44:55,040 --> 00:44:58,230
Even if we know the story's ending

840
00:44:58,890 --> 00:45:02,400
We still dare to pull on each other
a few more times

841
00:45:02,740 --> 00:45:06,910
There is a trial
worth being stubborn, worth writing

842
00:45:07,040 --> 00:45:11,400
That's the chapter we loved

843
00:45:14,030 --> 00:45:18,180
The brave person says goodbye first

844
00:45:18,280 --> 00:45:22,010
The love that's worth it
is always sorry

845
00:45:22,120 --> 00:45:25,830
Once we were bold and fearless,
fighting against the world

846
00:45:25,990 --> 00:45:29,440
Only later realizing
how small and pitiful we were

847
00:45:29,440 --> 00:45:33,550
If the ending could truly be seen

848
00:45:33,620 --> 00:45:37,350
Would we still dare to meet?

849
00:45:37,390 --> 00:45:40,920
As long as you say a time and place

850
00:45:40,920 --> 00:45:43,980
I will still show up,
no regrets, no complaints

851
00:45:44,060 --> 00:45:46,330
I would rather
